snippet.title: Mike Tyson Responds To Logan Paul Calling Him Out...
snippet.description:
Mike Tyson Responds To Logan Paul Calling Him Out...
The sports world has been having some...interesting...matchups as of late. For example, in the NBA, maybe of the "major favorites" have gone down and many stars have been injured, leaving who will take it all very up for grabs. Then, on the flipside of that, you have the world of boxing. Which has undergone a kind of "transformation" of sorts via the "celebrity boxing" that has been going on via the Paul Brothers and others that they have inspired. Jake and Logan Paul aren't afraid to flap their gums, and now, the words "fighting Mike Tyson" has come into play. We'll break it all down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation going on with Mike Tyson, Logan Paul, Jake Paul, Anderson Silva and everyone else who is being tied up into this madness involving boxing as of late. Are you amazed that so many big names are getting associated with potential fights for the Paul Brothers? Do you think this fad will ever truly end? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
